    <h2>Tom Lewis</h2>
    
    <h3>Personal Statement</h3>

    <p>A first-class graduate with nearly nine years of customer service experience with an aptitude for technology and a passion for learning and self-improvement, I undertake self-studying to advance my knowledge in technology and related fields such as Information Technology and Information Security. I use resources such as ITPro.TV and Udemy. My current employment with Tesco Mobile as a sales advisor allows me to practice and refine customer service skills, research skills and working with daily and weekly targets. My roles at Tesco and Tesco Mobile gave me invaluable experience of accountability, due diligence and working to a deadline.</p>

